---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Memorias" description="Memorias anuales de actividades y cuentas económicas del Centro Sociocultural Zaidín.">
  <section class="page-hero">
    <h1>Memorias</h1>
    <p class="subtitle">Memorias anuales de actividades y cuentas económicas</p>
  </section>

  <div class="page-content">
    <p>Para visibilizar la transparencia de nuestra Asociación os presentamos las memorias anuales de actividades de nuestro Centro Sociocultural Zaidín.</p>

    <h2>Memorias de actividades</h2>
    <div class="card-grid">
      <a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1VO4WRc6QBUfBJYnoXBniJ7JMfkHTCPe7/view" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="card" style="text-decoration:none">
        <h3 style="color:var(--green)">📄 Memoria actividades 2024</h3>
        <p style="color:var(--g500);font-size:0.9rem">Ver PDF</p>
      </a>
      <a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1F8RX4Y2eqcNFjY6tQ2UJ6MJtvVrMX5jX/view" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="card" style="text-decoration:none">
        <h3 style="color:var(--green)">📄 Memoria actividades 2023</h3>
        <p style="color:var(--g500);font-size:0.9rem">Ver PDF</p>
      </a>
      <a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1w3x4Ol6AXlJj7IThzuMW4lM6Ky7ytrrQ/view" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="card" style="text-decoration:none">
        <h3 style="color:var(--green)">📄 Memoria actividades 2022</h3>
        <p style="color:var(--g500);font-size:0.9rem">Ver PDF</p>
      </a>
      <a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1tCCW75WEVnBF-6wlOM27xSt0UWN5wBdo/view" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="card" style="text-decoration:none">
        <h3 style="color:var(--green)">📄 Memoria actividades 2021</h3>
        <p style="color:var(--g500);font-size:0.9rem">Ver PDF</p>
      </a>
      <a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1DTU9jVPZSmL5n1rox_rllX0MfKsQ1yJG/view" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="card" style="text-decoration:none">
        <h3 style="color:var(--green)">📄 Memoria actividades 2020</h3>
        <p style="color:var(--g500);font-size:0.9rem">Ver PDF</p>
      </a>
      <a href="https://documentcloud.adobe.com/link/review?uri=urn%3Aaaid%3Ascds%3AUS%3A83d1aa66-164a-4712-9839-fb44899dd000" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="card" style="text-decoration:none">
        <h3 style="color:var(--green)">📄 Memoria actividades 2019</h3>
        <p style="color:var(--g500);font-size:0.9rem">Ver PDF</p>
      </a>
    </div>

    <h2>Cuentas anuales</h2>
    <div class="card-grid">
      <a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/17qeoD8pHQ4xZaGRSDTsg0MMJIftlQZpD/view" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="card" style="text-decoration:none">
        <h3 style="color:var(--green)">💰 Cuentas anuales 2024</h3>
        <p style="color:var(--g500);font-size:0.9rem">Ver PDF</p>
      </a>
      <a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1gUQkGjgj3eCa7xHeLGyiu6BqmSxuLt0E/view" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="card" style="text-decoration:none">
        <h3 style="color:var(--green)">💰 Cuentas anuales 2023</h3>
        <p style="color:var(--g500);font-size:0.9rem">Ver PDF</p>
      </a>
      <a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1hxudvxO0rCOmF5PyZc58sKg0NZerZTJc/view" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="card" style="text-decoration:none">
        <h3 style="color:var(--green)">💰 Cuentas anuales 2022</h3>
        <p style="color:var(--g500);font-size:0.9rem">Ver PDF</p>
      </a>
      <a href="https://drive.google.com/file/d/1HOKprFXe85waIQh8poYSJ-deyq7PZ33_/view" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="card" style="text-decoration:none">
        <h3 style="color:var(--green)">💰 Cuentas anuales 2021</h3>
        <p style="color:var(--g500);font-size:0.9rem">Ver PDF</p>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>

<style is:global>
  .card-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: 0.75rem;
    margin-bottom: 2rem;
  }
  .card {
    background: var(--w);
    border: 1px solid var(--g200);
    border-radius: var(--r);
    padding: 1rem 1.25rem;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow);
    transition: box-shadow 0.2s;
  }
  .card:hover {
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-md);
    border-color: var(--green-light);
  }
  @media (min-width: 640px) {
    .card-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr); }
  }
  @media (min-width: 769px) {
    .card-grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); }
  }
</style>
